messages.message:
Everyone,

Today we’re releasing the *internal preview* of AI Hub. We’d love to get your feedback to help us address any issues and improve the user experience.

*What is included*
With the internal preview, you’d be able to use:
• *Converse App:* With Converse, users can have interactive conversations with their content, from documents to spreadsheets
• *Build Experience:* With Build, users can build applications to automate their repeatable workflows. 
• Loginless experience of Converse app. 
• Google sign in.  
• Usage based billing. 
We support all the file types supported in the Instabase platform - PDF, PNG, JPEG, JPG, CSV, DOCX, XLSX, HTML, TXT, EML, TIFF files etc.

*How to access*
Please visit aihub.instabase.com (http://aihub.instabase.com) to try out the internal preview. Log in with your @instabase.com (http://instabase.com) account.

DO NOT SHARE THIS WITH ANYONE OUTSIDE OF THE COMPANY!

*Feedback mechanism*
You can share your feedback with us through:
• *AI Hub Internal Preview Feedback  (https://docs.google.com/document/d/1ZiN9AO5NfdTFxSiBr4hGvqX97aox9l-CH5b_-D4Rcac/edit#)* doc to help collate and triage feedback. EMs and PMs will create project tickets and PFRs based on this. 
• *Slack:* You can also share any quick feedback in <#C0516UPPMT3|> channel. 
Try it out and let us know what you think!

AI Hub team
Congrats on yet another massive milestone! Onwards to launch! So great also to see everyone providing feedback! Really proud to be part of this team!
